<F P=100> Central-South Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   NPC Vice Chairman Fei Xiaotong Inspects Hainan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK2702022794 Haikou Hainan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2702022794 </F>
<F P=104>  Haikou Hainan People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yesterday afternoon [24 February], Du Qinglin, 
deputy secretary of the provincial party committee and chairman 
of the provincial people's congress standing committee, and Wang 
Xiaofeng, deputy secretary of the provincial party committee and 
executive vice governor, met at the Hainan Hotel with Fei 
Xiaotong, vice chairman of the National People's Congress 
Standing Committee, who was inspecting work in Hainan. 
  Du Qinglin and Wang Xiaofeng briefed Vice Chairman Fei 
Xiaotong on Hainan's economic growth, economic exploitation, 
economic structural reform, production, circulation, and other 
aspects of work over the past few years since Hainan Province 
was officially established. 
  Vice Chairman Fei Xiaotong spoke highly of each and every 
tremendous achievement scored by the hardworking Hainan people 
since Hainan Province was officially established. He also 
expressed the hope that Hainan will continue to further economic 
exploitation and construction and will strive to embark on a new 
stage of development. 

</TEXT>

