<H3> <TI>   Hebei People's Congress Session Opens 24 Feb </TI></H3>
<H4>   Leaders Attend Session </H4>
<F P=102> SK2602054194 Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 25 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2602054194 </F>
<F P=104>  Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] The Second Session of the Eighth Hebei 
Provincial People's Congress ceremoniously opened at the 
assembly hall of the Shijiazhuang No. 1 Workers Cultural Palace 
on 25 February. 
  Lu Chuanzan, Li Yongjin, Zhang Zhenhuan, Liu Zongyao, Dong 
Naifang, Hao Yongtang, Ning Quanfu, Wang Honglian, and Zhou Xin, 
executive members of the presidium of the session, were seated 
in the front line of the rostrum. Seated on the rostrum were 
Cheng Weigao, Ye Liansong, Li Bingliang, Li Wenshan, Ren Peiyu, 
Chen Yujie, Han Licheng, Chen Liyou, Xu Yongyue, Zhao Jinduo, Li 
Zhanshu, Li Haifeng, Guo Hongqi, Gu Erxiong, Wang Youhui, Liu 
Zuotian, Song Shuhua, Wang Zuwu, Zhang Runshen, Wang Shusen, 
Huang Lan, Du Benjie, Zhao Huichen, Ma Xinyun, Yu Zhenzhong, 
Wang Manqiu, Chen Hui, Zhao Yan, Han Shiqian, and (Yuan Ruxian). 
