members of the presidium were also seated on the rostrum. Also 
seated on the rostrum were Liu Bingyan, Zhang Shuguang, Xie 
Feng, Yin Zhe, Yang Zejiang, Guo Zhi, Yue Zongtai, Liu Ying, 
Hong Yi, Bai Shi, Pan Chengxiao, and Xu Chunxing. 
