<F P=100> Economic &amp; Agriculture </F>
<H3> <TI>   MOFTEC Revokes 2d Batch of Internal Documents </TI></H3>
<H4>   4th Batch of Documents Revoked </H4>
<F P=102> HK2401102094 Beijing GUOJI SHANGBAO in Chinese 8, 11 Jan 94 
p 4 </F>

<F P=103> HK2401102094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing GUOJI SHANGBAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

